						p We need our attorney to be utterly truthful with us and keep us on the right track, and we can absolutely depend on JC&amp;Company to fulfill that responsibility and look forward to a long-lasting relationship in our U.S. business. This is especially so as they are both law and accounting firm and we can get the one-stop legal and accounting service from them. Needless to say, it worked so efficiently so far and saved our time and costs.
						cite Sunguk Moon, CEO, Teamblind Inc

					blockquote
						p I was truly glad that I finally found a law firm I can trust and depend on, and this was especially important to me because, although our parent company had good reputation and resources in Korea, the business in the U.S. was completely new to me and all my company members. Simply put, They are impeccable professionals.
